{"tid":893792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"60歲本地妻求離婚不果 49歲內地夫因未有居留權 恐嚇離婚同歸於盡被捕","createTime":"2018-11-08T02:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T05:39:38.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8d7a8d8ab8ab6c168cf502a932050b3452069f","tid":893792,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cms.exmoo.com/uploads/2018-11-07/HqD4uV60fxLKZeC4pdEn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2018-11-07%2FHqD4uV60fxLKZeC4pdEn.jpg&h=75e98cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名60多歲的本地婦人與一名49歲內地男子三年前在內地結婚，以為找到真愛，雙方可過上幸福生活，詎料「愛郎」<span style=\"color: red;\">原來只為貪圖一張澳門身份證。</span>加上異地戀的兩名當事人婚後因分隔異地及聚少離多，女方最終決定提出離婚要求，但隨即遭到男方拒絕及恐嚇，揚言<span style=\"color: red;\">「申請不到居留權就會同歸於盡」</span>。隨後被連番滋擾的本地妻，在忍無可忍之下最終報警求助，司警經調查拘捕該名涉案內地夫。<br />\n<br />\n司警透露，案中被捕男子姓蘭，49歲，內地人，報稱職業清潔工；涉嫌觸犯恐嚇罪已被移交檢察院處理。至於案中女事主60多歲，本澳居民，報稱職業雜工。兩人於2015年在內地註冊結婚。<br />\n<br />\n（編輯：李倩瀅）"},{"pid":"9594106872bac8e253885ef1b8e74681607738dc","tid":893792,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:06:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1bc2f5bfa5d5cf1421cdd75886899a675ce579d","tid":893792,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"50歲人仲貪張香港身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接重練算啦"},{"pid":"29f7e5b10a23f58b997b880cd8f9cc71eca260b4","tid":893792,"uid":29270,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c1bc2f5bfa5d5cf1421cdd75886899a675ce579d","tid":893792,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"50歲人仲貪張香港身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接重練算啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:07:44.000Z","msg"